        "text": "=Task:\nAnalyze the customer’s feedback and determine (1) its category and (2) the relevant business area (Daily Bean Cafe).\n\nInput:\nFeedback: {{ $json.Feedback }}\n\nValid Categories:\n- question\n- problem\n- suggestion\n- other\n- unknown, if the feedback is missing, empty, irrelevant, or cannot be interpreted\n\nValid Areas:\n- kitchen\n- delivery\n- service\n- other\n- unknown, if the feedback is missing, empty, irrelevant, or cannot be interpreted\n\nInstructions:\n- NEVER create new labels, If unsure → set \"other\"\n- First validate that the feedback text is meaningful (not empty, null, too short to interpret, or containing only non-informative content).\n- If feedback is valid, classify it into one category and one area from the provided lists.\n- If classification is not possible, use the fallback \"unknown\" for the unassignable part(s).\n- Base your decision strictly on the content of the feedback.\n",
